%N A394448 a(n) is the smallest nonnegative integer whose first n hexadecimal digits coincide with its first n decimal digits.
%e A394448 1079648 expressed as hexadecimal number is 107960_16. It is the smallest number for which the first 5 digits coincide, so a(5)=1079648.
